relevant_findings.general: Well developed, well nourished in no acute distress.
relevant_findings.HEENT: Normocephalic, atraumatic, extraocular movements intact, anicteric.

relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes/rales/rhonchi, normal excursion, no respiratory distress.

relevant_findings.psychiatric: Normal judgment/insight, normal memory, normal mood/affect.
